{
  "id": "RAW_941b7fb7",
  "title": "ML Kit Prompt API｜赋能设备端 Gemini Nano，打造专属定制体验",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwODY4OTk2Mg==&mid=2652160482&idx=1&sn=240bbcfbfe780ae0882950ede1d2ef0c",
  "date": "2025-12-25 10:11:00",
  "author": "谷歌开发者",
  "siteName": "谷歌开发者",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"288\" data-backw=\"512\" data-imgfileid=\"504676825\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"512\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=42c8aba9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FrFWVXwibLGtzIyvb6w9tZhnbVd9WyQiaxgCzb0ibOmbsibrLicA5Q2nvsEQEicA9bdILLFBO9QkvffyIic4TCKbrC5ZTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkvhlx9csr\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkvhlxn1wej\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(147, 147, 147);font-style: italic;\">作者 / 开发者关系工程师 Caren Chang、软件工程师 Chengji Yan 和软件工程师 Penny Li</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 29.75px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv4k37dv5\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob1fx3\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI 正在助力打造个性化的应用体验，能够更轻松地将内容转化为最适合用户的形式。此前，我们已经针对特定用例 (如摘要和图像描述) 定制了&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv4k2j1m7s\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-size: 15px;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">ML Kit GenAI API</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob1fx3\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;来帮助开发者集成 Gemini Nano。</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4obdwy\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);font-size: 12px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv6j2o1e1a\"><span leaf=\"\">ML Kit GenAI API</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv48rc3jj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv6j2o1v7o\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\"><a href=\"https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2025/05/on-device-gen-ai-apis-ml-kit-gemini-nano.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2025/05/on-device-gen-ai-apis-ml-kit-gemini-nano.html</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob15y5\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而现在 Android 设备端生成式 AI 迎来了一个重要里程碑——我们正式推出&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">ML Kit GenAI Prompt API 的 Alpha 版本</span>。借助该 API，您可以向 Gemini Nano 发送自然语言和多模态请求，以满足使用生成式模型构建时对更高可控性和灵活性的需求。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 29.75px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv4oaetii\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv4o9q1um2\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-size: 15px;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">Kakao 等合作伙伴已经在使用 Prompt API 进行构建</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4obsmd\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，并打造出了具有实际落地价值的独特体验。仅用少量代码，您也可以立即体验 Prompt API 的强大功能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv4mvazby\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv6c5lrc5\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">Kakao 等合作伙伴已经在使用 Prompt API 进行构建</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv46rowpw\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv6c5l2ls\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\"><a href=\"https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2025/10/kakao-mobility-uses-gemini-nano-on.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2025/10/kakao-mobility-uses-gemini-nano-on.html</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">从预构建迈向自定义设备端 GenAI</span></strong></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob15gt\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Prompt API 突破了预构建功能的局限，支持自定义或特定于某个应用的 GenAI 用例，助您打造涉及复杂数据转换的独特功能。Prompt API 使用设备端 Gemini Nano 进行本地数据处理，在实现离线可用的同时，还能进一步强化用户隐私保护。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 67, 53);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Prompt API 的主要用例</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4obbjr\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Prompt API 能支持高度定制化的 GenAI 用例。以下是一些推荐的示例:</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4obq96\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">图像理解: 分析照片以进行分类 (例如，创建社交媒体帖子或识别 \"宠物\"、\"美食\" 或 \"旅行\" 等标签)。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob19zo\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">智能文档扫描: 使用传统的机器学习模型从收据中提取文本，然后使用 Prompt API 对每个项目进行分类。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob2kl\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">面向界面的数据转换: 基于对长篇内容的分析，提炼出简短、引人入胜的通知标题。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob1sdk\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">内容提示: 根据用户对主题的偏好，为新日记内容的主题提供灵感和建议。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob15nr\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">内容分析: 对客户评价进行情感倾向分析，如正面、中性或负面。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob24ti\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">信息提取: 从电子邮件往来记录中提取即将发生的活动关键信息。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: le f t;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 188, 4);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">实现 Prompt API</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4obtdz\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">使用 Prompt API，只需编写几行代码，即可创建自定义提示并设置可选的生成参数:</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"javascript\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__title\">Generation</span>.<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">getClient</span>().<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">generateContent</span>(</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">generateContentRequest</span>(</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ImagePart(bitmapImage),</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;TextPart(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"Categorize this image as one of the following: car, motorcycle, bike, scooter, other. Return only the category as the response.\"</span>),</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;) {</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">// Optional parameters</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;temperature =&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0.</span>2f</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;topK =&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">10</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;candidateCount =&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">1</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;maxOutputTokens =&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">10</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;},</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">)</span></code><br></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 29.75px;margin-bottom: 0px;text-indent: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 29.75px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv4ydc708\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob16et\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有关实现 Prompt API 的更详细示例，请查阅</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv4w00r50\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-size: 15px;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">官方文档</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob16et\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv4ycj14bh\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-size: 15px;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">Github 上的示例</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob16et\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv4x8b1jmn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv62gp16of\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">官方文档</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv43xncsh\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv62gp1mgp\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\"><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/ml-kit/genai/prompt/android\" target=\"_blank\">https://developers.google.com/ml-kit/genai/prompt/android</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv4zcohs\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv62gpx30\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">Github 上的示例</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv42rc1sr6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv62gp1wn8\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/googlesamples/mlkit/tree/master/android/genai\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/googlesamples/mlkit/tree/master/android/genai</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: le f t;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Gemini Nano、性能和原型设计</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4ob4dw\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前 Prompt API 在 Pixel 10 系列设备上表现最佳，该系列设备运行的是最新版本的 Gemini Nano (nano-v3)。此版本的 Gemini Nano 采用了我们在 I/O 大会上首次向开放模型社区发布的模型——Gemma 3n 同源的架构设计。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4obaxs\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同源的底层架构让开发者能更轻松地构建功能原型。即便对于没有 Pixel 10 设备的用户，同样可以在本地使用 Gemma 3n 来进行原型设计，即刻开始调试提示词。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 29.75px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv53cp23su\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4obfrp\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有关支持 GenAI API 的设备的完整列表，请参阅我们的</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv53c163d\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-size: 15px;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">设备支持文档</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkuu4obfrp\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv524aqa1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv5s151rvn\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\">设备支持文档</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;line-height: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjkv3zyc1icn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjkv3zxkr5l\" style=\"color: rgb(147, 147, 147);background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-size: 15px;font-weight: 400;font-style: normal;letter-spacing: 0.578px;word-spacing: 0px;text-shadow: none;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjkv5s151ae4\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/ml-kit/genai\" target=\"_blank\">https://developers.google.com/ml-kit/genai</a><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjkutuj7-9pcoxd\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#device</a>-support</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌发布 ML Kit GenAI Prompt API Alpha 版，允许开发者在 Android 应用中通过 Gemini Nano 实现自定义、高隐私保护的设备端生成式 AI 功能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌发布 ML Kit GenAI Prompt API Alpha 版，允许开发者在 Android 应用中通过 Gemini Nano 实现自定义、高隐私保护的设备端生成式 AI 功能。",
  "summary": "谷歌正式发布了 ML Kit GenAI Prompt API 的 Alpha 版本，标志着 Android 设备端生成式 AI 发展的重要里程碑。该 API 赋能开发者直接在 Android 应用中利用 Gemini Nano，实现低延迟、高隐私保护的定制化生成式 AI 功能。不同于之前针对特定用例的预构建 API，Prompt API 提供了更高的灵活性和可控性，支持开发者创建独特的、复杂的 GenAI 用例，如图像理解、智能文档扫描、面向界面的数据转换、内容提示和情感分析等。文章详细介绍了 Prompt API 的实现方式，包括通过少量代码即可创建自定义提示和设置生成参数，并强调了 Gemini Nano 在 Pixel 10 设备上的最佳性能，以及 Gemma 3n 模型在原型设计中的同源优势。谷歌鼓励开发者通过官方文档和 GitHub 示例开始集成。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "ML Kit GenAI Prompt API 赋能 Android 设备端定制化生成式 AI 应用。",
      "explanation": "此 API 的推出允许开发者直接在 Android 应用中集成 Gemini Nano，实现高度可定制的生成式 AI 功能，突破了以往预构建 API 的限制。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Prompt API 强调设备端处理，保障用户隐私和离线可用性。",
      "explanation": "通过利用设备本地的 Gemini Nano 模型，数据处理在设备上完成，从而增强了用户隐私保护，并支持应用在无网络连接的情况下运行 AI 功能。"
    },
    {
      "point": "API 支持多种定制化用例，提升应用的智能化水平。",
      "explanation": "开发者可利用 Prompt API 实现图像理解、智能文档扫描、内容提示、情感分析等功能，为用户提供更个性化、智能化的体验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Gemma 3n 模型可用于原型设计，降低开发门槛。",
      "explanation": "即使没有特定的 Pixel 10 设备，开发者也可以利用与 Gemini Nano 同源的 Gemma 3n 模型进行本地原型设计和提示词调试，加速开发进程。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Android 设备端生成式 AI 迎来重要里程碑——ML Kit GenAI Prompt API 的 Alpha 版本正式发布！借助该 API，您可以在 Android 应用中轻松构建低延迟、高隐私保护的定制化生成式 AI 功能。",
    "Prompt API 突破了预构建功能的局限，支持自定义或特定于某个应用的 GenAI 用例，助您打造涉及复杂数据转换的独特功能。",
    "Prompt API 使用设备端 Gemini Nano 进行本地数据处理，在实现离线可用的同时，还能进一步强化用户隐私保护。",
    "目前 Prompt API 在 Pixel 10 系列设备上表现最佳，该系列设备运行的是最新版本的 Gemini Nano (nano-v3)。"
  ],
